/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得自己好失敗<br />\n家庭關係又處理得差<br />\n男朋友又對自己愛理不理咁<br />\n班所謂朋友都係見高拜見低踩<br />\n好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"或許我不能完全了解你內心的痛苦，但我也曾置身於無助和絕望之中，明白身處痛苦是怎樣一回事。無論你的是否想放棄自己，也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存得太多太久，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你所能控制的程度。<br />\n<br />\n你不如停一停，到我們的網站           <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=ca447df9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>              。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"a332713939da32c5b11a0242c2ac1bd59ee42b67","tid":2156890,"uid":362366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8d0cda3362c622c4947b29b8e2401aff34806cd","tid":2156890,"uid":302374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e576ec62419cd3a54210f842e8888559315b8509","tid":2156890,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef071c5b61dffc6f09e8dcdc159faa8a50175a9c","tid":2156890,"uid":302374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:53:30.000Z","msg":"每次返屋企<br />\n老豆老母都好似唔太歡迎我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想我返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hk